cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SD

This paper involves the creation of an AI agent that learns to play a video game by training on internal memory states, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The game being played is Super Smash Bros. Melee, which involves graphics rendering (cs.GR) and potentially computer vision (cs.CV) if the AI is using visual cues to make decisions. The training process likely involves machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and the paper may also involve analysis of the data collected during training (cs.SD).
